Heidi, Heidi

7
00:00:32,530 --> 00:00:36,530
Because up here you are at home

8
00:00:36,530 --> 00:00:40,530
Dark fir trees

9
00:00:40,530 --> 00:00:44,530
Green meadows in the sunshine

10
00:00:44,530 --> 00:00:48,530
Heidi, Heidi

11
