The air is clean.

128
00:07:36,022 --> 00:07:38,022
Be quiet. It will be fine, child.

129
00:07:38,022 --> 00:07:40,022
Hopefully.

130
00:07:52,022 --> 00:07:55,022
We'll take the basket. It will definitely be a good bed.

131
00:07:55,700 --> 00:07:58,700
We just have to put something in it to make it soft.

132
00:07:58,700 --> 00:08:01,700
I've already found something, but we should put it in the room over there.

133
00:08:01,700 --> 00:08:03,700
There it is sunny and better for you.

134
00:08:03,700 --> 00:08:06,700
Oh yes, thank you. Here it is pretty. The sun is shining.

135
00:08:06,700 --> 00:08:08,700
And if she wants, she can see out of the window.

136
00:08:08,700 --> 00:08:13,700
Sebastian, I think it's a beautiful room for a cat, isn't it?

137
00:08:13,700 --> 00:08:16,700
Hopefully it's good enough.

138
00:08:16,852 --> 00:08:19,852
But you have a nice bed, my little kitten.

139
00:08:19,852 --> 00:08:21,852
Can you sleep in it?

140
00:08:21,852 --> 00:08:23,852
She stays in it, she seems to like it.

141
00:08:23,852 --> 00:08:25,852
This and that?

142
00:08:25,852 --> 00:08:27,852
We have to give her a name.

143
00:08:27,852 --> 00:08:30,852
Oh, I'm not particularly good at giving names, you know.

144
00:08:30,852 --> 00:08:33,852
But I have a nice name for her.

145
00:08:33,852 --> 00:08:35,852
What do you think, Mau Mau?

146
00:08:37,852 --> 00:08:40,852
Is she sleeping well? Now we have a secret.

147
00:08:40,852 --> 00:08:42,852
Nice. We must not tell anyone.

148
00:08:42,852 --> 00:08:45,748
And especially not in front of the Rottenmeier.

149
00:08:45,748 --> 00:08:49,248
It's your very, very dear cat. Don't you think so, Heidi?

150
00:08:49,248 --> 00:08:51,248
I think so, too.

151
00:09:02,256 --> 00:09:08,256
One moment, I'll be right done.

152
00:09:08,256 --> 00:09:11,256
And what can I do for you?

153
00:09:11,256 --> 00:09:13,256
Good morning.

154
00:09:13,256 --> 00:09:15,256
Already on your feet?

155
00:09:15,256 --> 00:09:17,256
Pssst.

156
00:09:17,256 --> 00:09:19,256
What is it?

157
00:09:19,256 --> 00:09:21,256
The breakfast for Mau Mau.

158
00:09:21,256 --> 00:09:24,256
Ah, that's what you're worried about, don't worry.

159
00:09:27,856 --> 00:09:31,856
This will taste good for you, and be careful, a rottenmeier.

160
00:09:31,856 --> 00:09:34,856
Wait a moment.

161
00:09:36,856 --> 00:09:38,856
My hat!

162
00:09:38,856 --> 00:09:42,856
No, no, no, my hat is better lifted. You trust me, don't you?

163
00:09:42,856 --> 00:09:45,820
Yes, you are dear, Sebastian.

164
00:09:45,820 --> 00:09:47,820
Mau, Mau?

165
00:09:51,820 --> 00:09:53,820
Mau, Mau!

166
00:09:55,820 --> 00:09:57,820
Mau, Mau!

167
00:10:05,820 --> 00:10:07,820
Mau, Mau!

168
00:10:11,820 --> 00:10:13,820
Mau, Mau, good morning, Mau, Mau.

169
00:10:15,820 --> 00:10:17,820
Mau, Mau!

170
00:10:18,096 --> 00:10:20,096
I asked for your breakfast.

171
00:10:20,096 --> 00:10:22,096
No, no.

172
00:10:28,144 --> 00:10:30,144
Don't you want to get out of there again?

173
00:10:30,144 --> 00:10:31,144
Ah!

174
00:10:31,144 --> 00:10:33,144
You don't do that, Momo!

175
00:10:38,128 --> 00:10:40,828
Your tongue tickles like that of Spendy and Bearly.

176
00:10:40,828 --> 00:10:42,828
But you can't know who that is yet.

177
00:10:50,828 --> 00:10:51,828
That tastes good.

178
00:10:54,328 --> 00:10:55,328
If you eat a lot...

179
00:10:55,344 --> 00:10:57,344
Now you're a big star!

180
00:11:06,448 --> 00:11:09,448
Oh, what did you do to your face?

181
00:11:09,448 --> 00:11:11,448
Oh, that. Maumau scratched me.

182
00:11:11,448 --> 00:11:14,448
That's just a scratch. It doesn't hurt at all.

183
00:11:14,448 --> 00:11:16,448
Oh, Maumau can scratch?

184
00:11:16,448 --> 00:11:19,448
All cats can scratch. That's why they have their claws.

185
00:11:19,448 --> 00:11:21,448
Oh, such a small one?

186
00:11:23,448 --> 00:11:24,448
Mademoiselle Clara!

187
00:11:24,448 --> 00:11:26,448
Oh, there comes Nettie. She mustn't know.

188
00:11:26,448 --> 00:11:28,448
Quickly, take her away!

189
00:11:28,448 --> 00:11:31,448
Maumau! Maumau, come quickly!

190
00:11:31,448 --> 00:11:32,448
This is no game!

191
